    <item>
      <title>由于复活节临近财政年度结束，日本市场面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/japanese-markets-face-risks-as-fiscal-year-end-falls-on-easter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着日本财政年度即将结束，许多全球市场因复活节休市，日本货币、股票和债券面临的风险正在不断增加。距离央行加息不到两周。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/japanese-markets-face-risks-as-fiscal-year-end-falls-on-easter</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 01:55:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国的房地产危机正在波及其最大的银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/china-s-property-crisis-is-rippling-through-its-biggest-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国持续的房地产低迷正在侵蚀该国最大的国有银行的资产负债表，因为它们的不良贷款率正在攀升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/china-s-property-crisis-is-rippling-through-its-biggest-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 01:46:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
